Violet Evergarden centres around Violet Evergarden, a former soldier who, after the war, becomes an "Auto Memory Doll" working to transcribe people's thoughts and emotions into written letters. The series delves into Violet's journey of self-discovery and emotional development as she grapples with understanding and expressing human emotions. Known for its breathtaking animation, intricate storytelling, and emotional depth, Violet Evergarden has been praised for its poignant exploration of the human condition and the power of words. The series has garnered widespread acclaim for its beautiful visuals and compelling narrative.

